{"tid":2114888,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊: 外國對「港版國安法」的認知深度淺得嚇人 質疑有人太快跳到「香港司法獨立已死」此極端說法","createTime":"2020-07-19T06:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T07:55:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4112535e1829e413e2e8d0e6b77c7f097f620151","tid":2114888,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:51:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/local/20200719/3R3ICR3CVD2TPSISTN62XADOIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200719%2F3R3ICR3CVD2TPSISTN62XADOIY%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB4jsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=2450a031\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200719%2F3R3ICR3CVD2TPSISTN62XADOIY%2F&h=8bba639e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/local/20200719/3R3ICR3CVD2TPSISTN62XADOIY/</a><br />\n<br />\n英國最高法院院長及香港終審法院非常任法官韋彥德發聲明，關注「港版國安法」，又指英國最高法院的法官會否續在終院擔任法官，要視乎香港能否維持司法獨立及法治，湯家驊在電台節目中回應指韋彥德聲明重點在於如何執行《國安法》，指即使法例條文寫得漂亮，若執行情況達不到維持高度自治，會令人擔心，但湯認為，「港版國安法」只是通過了兩周，質疑為何有人會跳到一個極端結果，指香港司法獨立已死，形容外國對「港版國安法」的認知深度淺得嚇人，港府責無旁貸要增加解說及透明度。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊強調，香港仍有司法獨立，透露當局很快會再委任一名現任英國最高法院法官出任終審法院非常任法官，湯強調，國家安全問題涉及政治問題及敏感資料，特首對有關資料的掌握會較清楚，因此有必要由特首指定法官審理有關案件。"},{"pid":"bd8264fe4e898e90e3dfaf95583e5f87358bbbaa","tid":2114888,"uid":21424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:52:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">11</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79aaa188cbd3e2c0240fa666d45f634c6183d29d","tid":2114888,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd8264fe4e898e90e3dfaf95583e5f87358bbbaa","tid":2114888,"uid":21424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"repl